title: Guy Code All Seasons + Specials 720p (1 - 2 - 3) [No Bonus Clips
description:
This torrent contains all 3 seasons of MTV's Guy Code.  They are all in 720p resolution except for two episodes (S01E10/S01E11).  The files were named according to MTV's episode list found here:
 <a href="
http://www.mtv.com/shows/guy_code/video.jhtml?filter=fulleps" rel="nofollow" target="_NEW">
http://www.mtv.com/shows/guy_code/video.jhtml?filter=fulleps</a>

Also please be aware that for some reason the last 3 specials the audio is slightly off-sync about halfway through.  My apologizes but I did the best I could and it literally took me hours as-is.  All the other episodes and the spring break special played perfectly when I tested with VLC.

I am planning on redoing the specials and also getting the bonus clips and making one big torrent in the future so keep an eye out for that.  Until then, enjoy!  I could only find season 1 on-line so that's why I put so much effort into bringing everyone this!
